# CloudPipe — AI Automation Platform

## Overview
CloudPipe 是一站式 AI 商業自動化平台，整合 Facebook Messenger、Telegram Bot 及多平台客服。

## Key Features
- Multi-channel Integration (Facebook, Telegram, WhatsApp)
- AI-Powered Customer Service
- Business Automation Workflows
- Real-time Analytics

